00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,500
And we got on...

261
00:15:15,539 --> 00:15:17,632
Tell me when.

262
00:15:17,675 --> 00:15:19,199
All right. Kick it over once.

263
00:15:20,444 --> 00:15:21,843
Yeah!

264
00:15:21,879 --> 00:15:23,506
Good job! Thank you.

265
00:15:23,547 --> 00:15:25,606
All right.

266
00:15:25,649 --> 00:15:27,617
Oh, thank you! Thank you!

267
00:15:27,651 --> 00:15:28,777
Oh, sure. Anytime, ma'am.

268
00:15:28,819 --> 00:15:30,047
You're such a smart boy!

269
00:15:30,087 --> 00:15:32,419
Well, not really.
It's very simple, actually.

270
00:15:32,456 --> 00:15:34,014
Oh, really? Thank you so much.

271
00:15:34,058 --> 00:15:35,355
Ok. Anytime.

272
00:15:35,393 --> 00:15:36,519
Hey, kid, come over here.

273
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:38,494
I want to talk to you.

274
00:15:38,529 --> 00:15:40,463
You want a job here this summer?

275
00:15:40,498 --> 00:15:42,398
Well, I don't know.

276
00:15:42,433 --> 00:15:43,559
Can I think about that?

277
00:15:43,601 --> 00:15:44,932
No. I just fired a kid.

278
00:15:44,969 --> 00:15:46,163
I need somebody right now.

279
00:15:46,203 --> 00:15:47,329
Do you want this job?

280
00:15:47,371 --> 00:15:48,998
Yeah. Yes.

281
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:50,632
I don't know.

282
00:15:50,674 --> 00:15:51,800
Say yes, Jeffrey.

283
00:15:51,842 --> 00:15:53,810
- All right. I'll take it.
- Ok! You got it!

284
00:15:53,844 --> 00:15:55,778
Now, look. This is car 68.

285
00:15:55,813 --> 00:15:58,247
It's in the west section.
Go get it.

286
00:15:58,282 --> 00:16:01,080
Carla, when I look at you...

287
00:16:01,852 --> 00:16:04,514
I think about
comic book heroines...

288
00:16:04,555 --> 00:16:06,682
like Wonder Woman...

289
00:16:06,724 --> 00:16:10,956
with her little tiny waist
and her big, beautiful... eyes...

290
00:16:10,995 --> 00:16:15,227
and her tiny little winged feet
